text: Otra Cosa ("Another Thing") is the fifth studio album by Mexican singer- songwriter Julieta Venegas. It was released worldwide on March 16, 2010. ==Track listing== Otra Cosa Más - EP (Walmart Exclusive)(only US) * "Bien o mal" * "Despedida" * "Debajo de Mi Lengua" * "Me Voy" * "Andar Conmigo" * "Limón y Sal" ==References== Category:2010 albums Category:Julieta Venegas albums Category:Spanish-language albums
title: Otra Cosa
